701057f-a.title: Bronx: Fort Independence St - Giles Place
701057f-a.text:
Port Independence Street, north side, west from Giles Place.
The street makes a sharp bend northward at Heath Avenue.
May 6, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
